  • Small tips for a successful network connection?

    1, 2.4 Ghz only Wi-Fi network

    2, Using BLE mode, turn on your phone's Bluetooth, our plug will automatically find it, and the Smart Life APP will pop up prompt for a connection

    3, The blink mode of the indicator corresponds connection method

  • How can I connect to my dual-band router?

    1, Please turn off 5GHz networking before first connecting

    2, Split the router network into two frequency bands of 2.4Ghz and 5ghz

    3, Purchase Eightree's exclusive 5GHz smart plugs directly: B0C5MN39C9, B0C9H2MK7T, B0C9GJJBR9

  • What should I do about after-sales issues?

    1, Contact the seller directly through the Amazon order

    2, Email to the after-sales email address on the box, state the problem and Amazon order number

  2. About Eightree

    Eightree is an up-and-coming brand established in 2021, dedicated to product development and manufacturing in the field of smart home. Our mission is to provide more convenient, high quality but affordable smart home solutions for people around the world.

    Smart home never needs to be expensive, just enjoy the convenience that smart home brings to your life. Eightree is always at your service.

      I absolutely love the EIGHTREE Smart Plugs! These little devices have made a huge difference in how I manage my home, and I cant recommend them enough. They are compatible with Alexa, Google Home, and SmartThings, making them incredibly easy to integrate into any smart... See more
      I absolutely love the EIGHTREE Smart Plugs! These little devices have made a huge difference in how I manage my home, and I cant recommend them enough. They are compatible with Alexa, Google Home, and SmartThings, making them incredibly easy to integrate into any smart home setup. With the ability to control them remotely via Wi-Fi and set timers, they have truly made life much easier and more efficient.

      Seamless Alexa & Google Home Compatibility Set up and control your devices with just your voice! Whether its turning on the coffee maker in the morning or adjusting the lights, these plugs work flawlessly with Alexa and Google Home.

      Wi-Fi Control from Anywhere These plugs connect to your home Wi-Fi (2.4GHz) and allow you to control any device plugged into them via the EIGHTREE app, even when youre not at home.

      Timer & Scheduling Function You can set schedules and timers to automate when devices turn on or off. This is perfect for things like lights, fans, or appliances that you want to operate on a schedule.

      Easy Setup & User-Friendly Setup is a breeze. You just plug in the smart plug, connect it to your Wi-Fi, and link it to your preferred smart assistant. I had everything running in under 10 minutes.

      4-Pack for Great Value The 4-pack gives you multiple plugs to outfit different areas of your home, whether its for lamps, kitchen appliances, or fans.

      These plugs work flawlessly with my devices, providing smooth remote control and automated scheduling. I use them to turn off the lights when I forget or schedule the fan to turn on before I wake up. The EIGHTREE app is intuitive, and the setup process was very straightforward. The voice control feature makes everything even more convenientI never have to get up to turn things off again!

      Pros:
      Works seamlessly with Alexa, Google Home, and SmartThings
      Wi-Fi enabled for remote control, even when youre not at home
      Timer and scheduling features for ultimate convenience
      Simple setup with an intuitive app
      4-pack provides excellent value for your money

      Cons:
      Only supports 2.4GHz Wi-Fi, so make sure your network is compatible
      No energy monitoring features, though this isnt a dealbreaker for me
